OL,3,CEx-BBC presenter Huw Edwards pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to making indecent images of
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FHuw Edwards has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fthree counts of making indecent images
OL,9,Fof children.
OL,11,FThe BBC has said the former presenter
OL,12,Fwould have been sacked had he been
OL,13,Fcharged over accessing indecent images
OL,14,Fwhile still working for the
OL,15,Fcorporation, adding that it was
OL,16,F"shocked" at his "abhorrent behaviour".
