OL,3,CEx-BBC presenter Huw Edwards pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to making indecent images of
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FWestminster Magistrates Court heard
OL,8,Fthe 62-year-old had been involved in
OL,9,Fonline chat with an adult man on
OL,10,FWhatsApp between December 2020 and
OL,11,FAugust 2021, who sent him 377 sexual
OL,12,Fimages, of which 41 were indecent
OL,13,Fimages of children.
OL,15,FThe bulk of these, 36, were sent
OL,16,Fduring a two-month period.
