OL,7,FThe final indecent image was sent in
OL,8,FAugust 2021, a category A film
OL,9,Ffeaturing a young boy.
OL,11,FThe man told Edwards the boy was quite
OL,12,Fyoung looking, and that he had more
OL,13,Fimages which were illegal.
OL,15,FEdwards told him again to not to send
OL,16,Fany illegal images, the court was told.
OL,18,FNo more were sent, and the pair
OL,19,Fcontinued to exchange legal
OL,20,Fpornographic images until April 2022.
