OL,7,F"It is only the images that are the
OL,8,Fsubject of the charges that came via a
OL,9,FWhatsApp chat.
OL,11,F"Mr Edwards did not keep any images,
OL,12,Fdid not send any to anyone else and
OL,13,Fdid not and has not sought similar
OL,14,Fimages from anywhere else."
OL,16,FAfter Edwards pleaded guilty to the
OL,17,FBBC issued a lengthy statement saying
OL,18,Fthey were "shocked" by what was heard
OL,19,Fin court adding "there can be no place
OL,20,Ffor such abhorrent behaviour and our
OL,21,Fthoughts are with all those affected."
