OL,3,CEx-BBC presenter Huw Edwards pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to making indecent images of
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FThe BBC said they were made aware in
OL,8,FNovember 2023 Edwards had been
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of serious
OL,10,Foffences, they said they had also been
OL,11,Ftold about a "significant risk to his
OL,12,Fhealth."
OL,14,FThe corporation added that if he had
OL,15,Fever been charged while employed by
OL,16,Fthe BBC they would have immediately
OL,17,Fdismissed him.
OL,19,FEdwards left the BBC in April. He was
OL,20,Fcharged on July 29.
