OL,7,FSentencing guidelines set the starting
OL,8,Fpoint for any jail term for possession
OL,9,Fof a Category A image at 12 months,
OL,10,Fwith a range of 26 weeks to three
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FThe starting point is 26 weeks for a
OL,14,Fcategory B image, and a community
OL,15,Forder for category C, he said.
OL,17,FEdwards was bailed and will be
OL,18,Fsentenced at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on September 16.
